                <h1>Master Document Formatting: Essential Tips & Techniques</h1>
                <p>Document formatting encompasses various groups and techniques essential for achieving visually appealing and organized text. It includes paragraph alignment, font selection, spacing, and the use of headers and footers. Mastering these elements enhances readability and professionalism in written documents, making communication more effective.</p>
